title: EastEnders spoiler: Max brings his scheming into Queen Vic crisis
text:
EastEnders spoiler: Max brings his scheming into Queen Vic crisis What has Max got planned for Albert Square Share Comments By Joshua Haigh 18:37, 24 FEB 2017 TV What's going to happen? soaps On tonight's episode of EastEnders there's more bad news for the Queen Vic.
Mick gets told that the ceiling is in desperate repair and needs to be dealt with immediately.
He becomes concerned when he realises how much it's going to cost him.
Thankfully, Konrad kindly offers to do all the world for half of the price.

(Photo: BBC) Jack gets involved and offers Mick a lifeline, but Max ends up giving him second thoughts.
Could Max be up to his scheming again?
In the meantime, Konrad decides to invite Shirley out for a slap up meal.
Elsewhere on the Square, Denise speaks to a journalist at the Gazette about the state of the local community.
(Photo: BBC) Ian becomes self-conscious when he realises he's put on some weight.
He chats with Jane and they both end up agreeing that he could make an effort to be healthier.
Meanwhile, Louise, Madison and Alexandra end up annoying Bex again.
